sun.jvm.hotspot.debugger.win32.coff

Interface AuxSymbolRecord

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AuxBfEfRecord, AuxFileRecord, AuxFunctionDefinitionRecord, AuxSectionDefinitionsRecord, AuxWeakExternalRecord

    public interface AuxSymbolRecord
    Describes an Auxiliary Symbol Record. Such records may follow a Symbol Table record. (Some of the descriptions are taken directly from Microsoft's documentation and are copyrighted by Microsoft.)
